quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  50,16,"Walaqad khalaqna al-insanawanaAAlamu ma tuwaswisu bihi nafsuhu wanahnu aqrabuilayhi min habli alwareed"
  50,17,"Ith yatalaqqa almutalaqqiyaniAAani alyameeni waAAani ashshimali qaAAeed"
  50,18,"Ma yalfithu min qawlinilla ladayhi raqeebun AAateed"
  50,19,"Wajaat sakratu almawti bilhaqqithalika ma kunta minhu taheed"
  50,20,"Wanufikha fee assoori thalikayawmu alwaAAeed"
  50,21,"Wajaat kullu nafsin maAAaha sa-iqunwashaheed"
  50,22,"Laqad kunta fee ghaflatin min hathafakashafna AAanka ghitaaka fabasarukaalyawma hadeed"
  50,23,"Waqala qareenuhu hatha maladayya AAateed"
  50,24,"Alqiya fee jahannama kulla kaffarinAAaneed"
  50,25,"MannaAAin lilkhayri muAAtadin mureeb"
  50,26,"Allathee jaAAala maAAa Allahiilahan akhara faalqiyahu fee alAAathabiashshadeed"
  50,27,"Qala qareenuhu rabbana maatghaytuhu walakin kana fee dalalinbaAAeed"
  50,28,"Qala la takhtasimooladayya waqad qaddamtu ilaykum bilwaAAeed"
  50,29,"Ma yubaddalu alqawlu ladayya wamaana bithallamin lilAAabeed"
  50,30,"Yawma naqoolu lijahannama hali imtala/tiwataqoolu hal min mazeed"
  50,31,"Waozlifati aljannatu lilmuttaqeena ghayrabaAAeed"
  50,32,"Hatha ma tooAAadoona likulliawwabin hafeeth"
  50,33,"Man khashiya arrahmanabilghaybi wajaa biqalbin muneeb"
  50,34,"Odkhulooha bisalamin thalikayawmu alkhulood"
  50,35,"Lahum ma yashaoona feehawaladayna mazeed"
